  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.8.2">
<l>ammā ṉāyppiṉṉu</l>
<l>memmāṇ pumāṉāṉa</l>
<l>vemmā vāykīṇṭa</l>
<l>cemmā kaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even after being the father</l>
<l>he is Kṛṣṇa with large red eyes</l>
<l>who split the mouth of the cruel horse</l>
<l>who was our glorious man.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
